OL,3,CDebt-ridden funeral firm faces winding
OL,4,Cup order amid police probe
OL,6,FThirty-five bodies have been removed
OL,7,Ffrom its premises in Hessle Road. Two
OL,8,Fpeople have been arrested on suspicion
OL,9,Fof fraud and preventing a lawful burial
OL,11,FSeparate to the criminal inquiry, Hull
OL,12,FCity Council has confirmed it has
OL,13,Fissued a winding up petition.
OL,15,FThe authority said it was "not
OL,16,Funusual" for undertakers to owe money
OL,17,F"as they await payments from families
OL,18,Fwho have lost loved ones", but Legacy
OL,19,Fhad accrued mounting debts.
