OL,3,CDebt-ridden funeral firm faces winding
OL,4,Cup order amid police probe
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "It became
OL,7,Fapparent in February of last year that
OL,8,Fthe debt owing to the council by
OL,9,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors
OL,10,FLtd was becoming significant, so the
OL,11,Fcouncil obtained a county court
OL,12,Fjudgement of #51,508.46, in relation
OL,13,Fto unpaid fees and charges, including
OL,14,Fcremation fees.
