OL,3,CDebt-ridden funeral firm faces winding
OL,4,Cup order amid police probe
OL,6,F"A payment arrangement was put in
OL,7,Fplace, with the last payment being
OL,8,Fmade to the Council on 2 February
OL,9,F2024. The remaining debt is now
OL,10,F#40,938.08. We are exploring options
OL,11,Fto recoup that sum, and have issued a
OL,12,Fpetition to wind up the company."
OL,14,FA winding up petition is a legal
OL,15,Fnotice that creditors file with the
OL,16,Fcourts requesting that they have a
OL,17,Fhearing to establish whether the
OL,18,Fdebtor company is insolvent. The
OL,19,Fwinding up petition begins the
OL,20,Fcompulsory liquidation process.
